Features
--------
1 - You can create new blog posts
2 - You can edit the blog posts you made
3 - You can view the blog posts present
4 - You can share the blog post links and yes they update in the database
    how many times that link has been visited you can check it out in the database
5 - You can also search your blog posts for title, author, preview text, and body
6 - Enjoy :D
7 - For further questions please email me at josephaasaad@gmail.com
